---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout>
  <article class="py-12 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white shadow-lg rounded-lg my-auto">
    <header class="mb-6 p-5 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold text-brand-blueFinca mb-4">Terms and Conditions</h2>
      <meta name="description" content="Check the terms and conditions of our property management and vacation rental services." />
    </header>

    <section class="space-y-8 p-5">
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Welcome to our property management and vacation rental management company. Below are the terms and conditions governing the use of our services. By using our services, you agree to comply with these terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-blueFinca">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        By accessing or using our services, you agree to be bound by these terms and conditions. If you disagree with any part of these terms, you must not use our services.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-blueFinca">2. Services Offered</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        Our company offers property management services, vacation rental management, and related advisory services. We handle all the necessary operations to ensure that the properties are managed efficiently and professionally.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-blueFinca">3. User Responsibility</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        As a user of our services, it is your responsibility to provide accurate and truthful information when contracting our services. You are also responsible for ensuring that the properties comply with all applicable legal regulations.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-blueFinca">4. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        All content and materials related to our services, including texts, images, logos, and trademarks, are the exclusive property of our company or its licensors. Unauthorized reproduction is prohibited.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-blueFinca">5. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        We will not be liable for direct, indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from the use or inability to use our services.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-blueFinca">6. Modifications</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Any changes will be posted on this page with the date of the last update.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-brand-blueFinca">7. Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
        If you have any questions about these terms, please feel free to contact us through the available channels on our contact page.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</Layout>
